name: Starter kit & Tool kit
description:
I have been a mess when starting out a project. I really just jump back and forth on different files just to fetch the necessary things I needed. Then I decided to create a mega file kit for myself ( and now I'm sharing to the community). It's a mega kit that I created which composed of things I use always when working with designs.


It has the following (one of these that would be missing I'll be in armageddon mode):

  • File organizing
  • Components
  • Userflow kit
  • Sitemap kit
  • Styleguide and asset
  • Sprint
  • Grid Systems


Hope you guys would love this! Please do share your thoughts on how I could improve on this! <3
